{"tid":141019,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"英國戲院致敬奧斯卡 先播La La Land廿秒再播Moonlight","createTime":"2017-03-02T15:00:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-03T06:32:42.000Z","uid":41343,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"20241ef65f1711c6a9606e6b2cd22ea5016b72e7","tid":141019,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T15:00:07.000Z","msg":"繼第 89 屆奧斯卡把本該獲得最佳影片獎的《月光下的藍色男孩》（Moonight），誤頒給了同樣也是大熱門的《樂來越愛你》（La La Land）之後，網路上開始流傳了許多有趣的惡搞圖片，即便這個插曲實在讓得獎者、入圍者、現場觀眾以及電視機前的觀眾都相當錯愕，事件過後大家也抱持著相當輕鬆的心情（有嗎？），也認定明年奧斯卡肯定會有非常多相關這起事件的玩笑。<br />\n<br />\n日前在倫敦的里約電影院，在一場滿場的《月光下的藍色男孩》放映中，一開始先放了 20 秒的《樂來越愛你》，然後再換回本來的《月光下的藍色男孩》，現場的觀眾立刻理解這個舉動的笑點，在電影院響起了如雷的掌聲。戲院的經理在採訪中表示：<br />\n<br />\n「我們並不是放真的《樂來越愛你》正片，而是預告裡面的幾秒，然後我們就把它關掉，用很笨拙的方式，讓大家認為我們不小心放錯了。」<br />\n<br />\n里約戲院因為《月光下的藍色男孩》獲獎，特別多放映了此片一個禮拜，不僅里約戲院，就在此片獲得三項奧斯卡獎後，在英國的票房飛快成長，相信在台灣也能獲得同樣的優異成績。《月光下的藍色男孩》將會在 2017 年 3 月 3 &nbsp;日於台灣盛大上映。"},{"pid":"680f0285cc56ccd45d84ba587bc7ea58681186e7","tid":141019,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T15:46:00.000Z","msg":"如果香港戲院咁樣播法....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d3e9f03adcea5918e0a2393d0ce0c4aaaa96d25","tid":141019,"uid":83799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T15:52:38.000Z","msg":"抽水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be1acca9104b78ba19c76f1dbdc779228f4fa605","tid":141019,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T16:11:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f26d6b1bfca4791a0cfb7bd97ac1f53df4e0b56b","tid":141019,"uid":71219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T16:21:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"323203c0449d0903669d1feb7a033d247da58605","tid":141019,"uid":38172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T16:25:41.000Z","msg":"幽默感既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9b54cdd5f1ab0ad6ba59d38bf728c378fc1a8eb","tid":141019,"uid":34427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T06:32:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}